_data.text:
Empower your NuxtJS application with `@nuxtjs/content` module: write in a `content/` directory and fetch your Markdown, JSON, YAML and CSV files through a MongoDB like API, acting as a **Git-based Headless CMS**.

## Writing content

Learn how to write your `content/`, supporting Markdown, YAML, CSV and JSON: https://content.nuxtjs.org/writing.

## Fetching content

Learn how to fetch your content with `$content`: https://content.nuxtjs.org/fetching.

## Displaying content

Learn how to display your Markdown content with the `<nuxt-content>` component directly in your template: https://content.nuxtjs.org/displaying.

_data.title: The Technical Debt in Seismology
_data.description: Most basic tools in seismology are written in the 90s, modernization of these would lower the barrier for multi-disciplenary scientists and curious people

children.value: Seismology is an old science, even the ancient Chinese knew that earth was shaking in specific directions. Up until the 60s, seismology didn't have proper instrumentation. Birth of digital seismometers in the 80s was a major leap forward for the field. Suddenly the scientists were drowning in data. The sudden need for computational resources was driven creation of many of the basic softwares and most of these are still being used today and that is a problem.

_data.text:
Seismology is an old science, even the ancient Chinese knew that earth was shaking in specific directions. Up until the 60s, seismology didn't have proper instrumentation. Birth of digital seismometers in the 80s was a major leap forward for the field. Suddenly the scientists were drowning in data. The sudden need for computational resources was driven creation of many of the basic softwares and most of these are still being used today and that is a problem.
